# Used by `dart pub publish` for the `influto` package. The companion `influto_iap`
# (the flutter_iap/ directory) is published as its OWN package — exclude it here so it
# isn't bundled inside `influto`. The rest mirrors .gitignore (build/tooling artifacts).
flutter_iap/

